Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}絢爛奪目 不堪直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的衝動 因為你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窺探 想知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真實的心請允許我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}數著星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你與我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}兒時仰望天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔誠祈禱的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願與你攜手去往無限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成為導航未來之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在保護Megafauna號逃離Capital特區的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我收穫了自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒有等它派上用處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,變化又一個個接踵而至
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只能拼盡全力去適應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到底哪條路 才通向真正的明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙戰爭爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,本艦進入環地球軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,檢查氣密狀況 不許馬虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,出擊前的機體最需要哪些保養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用腦子好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加固塗層時需要施壓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,注意保持厚度均勻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把塗層嵌進凹陷處加壓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就能和船體材質同化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,認真干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,非要說G-Self做這個比較快的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,危不危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼用力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想敲出洞來麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,修理工具的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不同於武器 戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你亂動…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,才越捆越緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,諾貝魯 拉萊雅如果逃走的話要報告我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再上甲板摟住G-Self 問題可就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那確實頭疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說火蠑螈號率領的先頭部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,出發前往Capital塔了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞的國家電視台是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,去阻止火蠑螈號的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,您說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈號的戰鬥指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果落到那個把亞美利亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,當作私兵的青年人手裏 會沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,關於尼肯寧總統兒子的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不能妄下定論…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,佔領Capital塔行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有實施的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因為Capital軍已經嚴陣以待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對 反對宇宙戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 生命體征下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這架滑翔機的導航系統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,會直接把我帶回紐約克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,總統如果真的下令出動宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是對我統帥權的踐踏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是亞美利亞國家電視台播出的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那應該是針對Capital軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,與我們塔管無關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔真的不會有危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是亞美利亞也不敢觸犯這種禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,梅莎美 脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,格裏夫博爾 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉 情況良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,勒格森 跟蹤正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,筆直下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,展現MackKnife性能的機會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 兩艘艦艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把所有Capital塔上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都當成了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,星艦Garanden
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,和海上相比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還是這樣更威風凜凜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,面具這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把新機從Capital塔直接運來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,讓人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}沒想到這麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}性能值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}長相不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}關性能什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在下將用這架MackKnife一雪連敗的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}噢噢！面具 面具 面具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵清理甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 昆珀上校和茹甘司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,效率真是高的離譜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕漏掉一根螺絲 一個橡皮圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都會對機體造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你也習慣了這裏的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,MackKnife運來的集裝箱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,由你負責整理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人有兩艘戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,戰術會議室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,盧因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明明應該在為昆達拉的榮譽而戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的機槍演習是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一架滑翔機也擊落不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,作為大隊長我感到恥辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 噢 噢 噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下面介紹的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,第二小隊的米克·傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果佔領Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,世界和Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,都將臣服於亞美利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,屆時世界的女王就是米克·傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而國王則是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是大隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,總統 我們支持你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是你們中最戰功卓著的那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和海盜船上相比 簡直變了個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,使喚那些駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候就得靠哄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這支由亞美利亞自行建造的宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅將終結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我國與貢德梵之間曠日持久的大陸戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還將成為亞美利亞稱霸宇宙與地球的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,作戰計劃之關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拉特爾·拜森旗下艦隊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,總統閣下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是宇宙艦隊的出擊儀式！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}古匈總監
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼現在才來？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,之前你到哪裏幹什麼去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去見證我國優秀的間諜組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所提供的「事實真相」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,事實真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 儘管Capital塔被軍隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以Capital塔為踏板 轉而進攻貢德梵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這是閣下親自擬定的計劃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這我無法否認…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但為何命令火蠑螈號在此時出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,況且未經過我的許可！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你外出時情報顯示Capital軍佔領軌道塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我以總統權限下令出擊有何不妥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就請您撤銷命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙艦隊擔任後方支援的特別號令已經下達！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我個人意願可以左右的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,無法撤銷命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是軍人 服從命令是天職
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為維護亞美利亞帝國的威信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,結束Capital塔的壟斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還世界以自由吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈號與巨鱷級的追蹤目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,本艦Garanden和海盜船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,警告機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,若遠離Capital塔 將無法返回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,您什麼時候到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,和法皇大人一起 乘坐同一班艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏馬上就會炮火紛飛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我有義務見證面具部隊的戰鬥過程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞軍臨陣打造的宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看我如何把尼肯寧總統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那只傲慢的鼻子擰下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Megafauna上天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說貝魯利也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 法皇大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利和艾達乘坐的Megafauna上了宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self是從宇宙下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯是我養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不會給別人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,原來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈總監說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以在聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,將宇宙臍帶教法皇扣為人質 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這次遲到還值得原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是 您說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我兒子克裏姆指揮的火蠑螈號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有這樣一支艦隊護衛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,相比之下 剛組建的Capital軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,從環地球航線進入衛星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下面去往哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以最大角度前往聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,胡來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為分散Capital軍兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,將法皇扣為人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也不失為一種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話 就無回頭路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人可到不了火蠑螈號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我有做宇宙海盜的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}拉萊雅脫逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼被你解開的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ousia和Catsith負責艦船護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ousia 出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,別擋著MackKnife
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘司令開口便是前後夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是我們的第一次宇宙戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是 芭拉拉·佩歐茹 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,即便Garanden出動機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我先攻Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就不得不分兵救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還能有什麼辦法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,迎擊就由我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有勞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 Hecate坐鎮火蠑螈號後方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好好陪Garanden來的客人玩上一把！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈號上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,切 米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和敵人相距一個標準戰鬥距離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Garanden出動的機動戰士部隊行動古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來遲一步 但不能退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔也出動了機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Garanden從後面夾擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐別去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下留下保護Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,盧安 連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的傢伙就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽不見 我聽不見！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙用背包 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,會陷入混戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,請在這裏狙擊漏網的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說得有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不許打中Capital塔和自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼停火？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 雙方在站前打成一團了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,撒了米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,…就意味著會被近身幹掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙裏逃跑還用翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次宇宙戰 像蝴蝶般飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像蜜蜂般出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是天才克裏姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,米克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Garanden的部隊在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們同時出擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,應該在背後才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到哪裏去了 Capital軍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,通知Capital塔部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有機動戰士從海盜船方向來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是它？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是Capital衛隊的Recksnow嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,當我的擋箭牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是從海盜船上起飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你這機體又是那支部隊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這個Capital衛隊的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這人怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,海盜船也應該看得懂光信號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,光信號？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的機動戰士在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,交出G-Self和拉萊雅的話就停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,G和拉萊雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,動手？ 還是不動？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,擋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,手指也是槍身？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,說你呢 G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就把凱爾貝斯中尉的Recksnow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原樣奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,繩索？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果是實彈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經當場斃命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,現在投降無話可說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果交出拉萊雅·曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放過你也未嘗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,頭盔裏還戴著面具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它內藏數據和感應裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅還沒恢復記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,踹飛這個面具佬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,盧安？ 奧利瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個跳級生走到哪裏都壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,脅迫Megafauna…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅還在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,面具這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅在船上無法攻擊Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這台宇宙用背包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,反應速度真快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,背包外加Megafauna嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,根本無從下手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓艾達小姐加入宇宙戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,光束衰減
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼打不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是我失誤還是對手太厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉 退後！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,被發光體騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,面具！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}切斷短路的電源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他們真的說要拉萊雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以敵人不攻擊Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是難保不被流彈打中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要當心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼當心？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,變形會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,成為破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉 是G-Self幹得？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 沒有拿下Megafauna…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,發信號召回機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裏前往Capital塔的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,必須重返環地球軌道 現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因為Megafauna的中途攪局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Garanden的機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和Megafauna意外接戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但無功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是Capital軍在宇宙中的初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,全暈得找不到北了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那的確不能怪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和Megafauna交手一敗塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是在下的疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了低軌道空戰的特殊性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是昆珀上校的來電
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,轉交給面具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉的MackKnife傷痕纍纍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,面具部隊的默契度 看來還有待提高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,初陣便要他們執行前後夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,遭報應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,報應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經下令Garanden
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,直接開往聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是為了保護法皇不受宇宙人的威脅咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達也返航了對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 G-Self也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有任何損失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們艦隊直接前往聖波爾圖 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是 補給艦也即將抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,本艦拉特爾·拜森旗下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,五艘鱷魚級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,將先於Capital塔冠艇抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,果然非同凡響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,荷米斯玫瑰設計圖的造物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈總監將率領亞美利亞宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,前往聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,聖波爾圖…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital塔最上層的站點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是交接光子電池的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊登陸那裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,會因為觸犯最大的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,遭到報應的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,報應？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,報應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真那麼做的話當然會遭報應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她說宇宙 她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哈朋先生想方設法強化G-Self的武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上艾達小姐的慫恿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想試著用好它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,結果被綁著送上聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在大聖堂裏看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽 法皇和…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 G之復國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,佔領Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見的敵人好可怕
